  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>ADMIN ASSISTANT</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· To handle general administrative duties such as attending to phone calls, email correspondence, filing of documentation &amp; data entry etc</p>\n<p>· To handle administrative duties in Admin/HR department ie. Company’s insurances renewals, direct workers’ administrative work scope preferably with some experience in workers’ wages computation etc</p>\n<p>· To provide administrative work support to Admin/Accounts/Procurement Departments etc</p>\n<p>· Any other ad hoc duties as assigned by Superior or Management</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>· GCE ‘O’, GCE ‘A’ Level, Diploma in Business Administration or relevant Degree equivalent</p>\n<p>· Administrative with reception experience, preferably related to Construction Industry, would be an added advantage</p>\n<p>· PC literate &amp; bilingual with good interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>· Meticulous, responsible &amp; possess a good working attitude</p>\n<p>· Candidates without experience are welcome to apply</p>",
